items.display_name: Earth's Best Organic Mini Blueberry Waffles
items.details: 32 Mini Waffles (8 sets of 4). All natural. Whole Grain - 10 g or more per serving. Excellent source of iron, zinc and six B vitamins. USDA organic. Let's make a great start to a lifetime of good health! New Earth's Best Sesame Street frozen children's foods are all-natural superior nutrition that's convenient for parents, and delicious and fun for young children. Whole Grain Organic Mini Waffles contain 10 g whole grain per serving, and are made with no artificial flavors, colors or preservatives, or potentially harmful pesticides. Specially formulated with iron, zinc and six B vitamins, and no genetically engineered ingredients, hydrogenated oils or trans fat. Blueberry fun! As a healthy alternative to syrup, provide your children with low-fat yogurt to spread on top of their waffles. Top with some colorful slices of fruit! Circle shape hunt! Point to the waffles and ask your children, what shape are these waffles? Then, after breakfast, encourage them to look for other objects that are shaped like a circle! Check out the Earth's Best difference. Organic ingredients grown without potentially harmful pesticides. No genetically engineered ingredients. Whole grains that are not stripped of their naturally occurring nutrients. Iron to help transport oxygen throughout your body. Zinc to boost your body's ability to fight infection. B Vitamins to unlock energy in carbohydrates. Help your child make healthy habits an important and fun part of everyday life! Healthy habits for life - a great start to a lifetime of good health. The Whole Grain Difference: Organic mini waffles contain 10 g whole grain per serving, and are made with organic whole wheat flour. Our grains are grown without potentially harmful pesticides. The whole wheat flour used in Organic Mini Waffles contain all 3 layers of the grain when processed, making it rich in mineral, vitamin and fiber value as compared to those that are refined. Certified Organic by Quality Assurance International (QAI). Made in Canada.

items.details: Made with natural ingredients. GF: Certified gluten-free. 125 calories per serving. 6 g fiber per serving. 9 g protein per serving. Gluten-free. Lactose-free. Yeast-free. Egg-free. Oil-free. Preservative-free. Nourishment Defined: Our line of flour-free waffle products reflects our philosophy that simple is better. The following wholesome ingredients are at the heart of our waffles and account for over 1/2 of our product weight. Silken soy puree, produced from soybeans, a nutritious plant-based protein. Gluten-free rolled oats, a hearty whole grain found in our waffles that sustains you longer. Coconut milk, a tasty and nutritious ingredient that helps us naturally achieve a great tasting, savory waffle. Chia seeds, famous since the days of the Aztec warriors, these super seeds provide energy to help you fight through your day. Our mission is simple. To provide the highest quality products, using the purest and simplest ingredients. We think less is more. Less ingredients, less fillers. More tasty, more filling! These delicious waffles are made with natural ingredients, yielding a product that is full of flavor, not flour. Our waffles are not only flour-free and protein enriched, (containing 80% more protein than an average waffle) but they are also free of gluten, lactose, yeast, egg, oil and preservatives. To learn more, please visit www.frozenguru.com.
items.directions: Keep frozen. Recommended Preparation: Toaster Oven - Toast on a low setting for 3-5 minutes or simply wait for the savory coconut aroma to fill your kitchen. Alternative Preparation: Microwave - Microwave waffles individually for 30-45 seconds.
items.ingredients: Silken Soy Puree (Filtered Water, Whole Non-GMO Soybeans, Magnesium Chloride, Calcium Chloride), Filtered Water, Gluten-Free Rolled Oats, Applesauce (Apples, Ascorbic Acid), Whey Protein Isolate, Chia Seeds, Ground Flaxseeds, Potato Starch, Coconut Milk Powder, Soy Lecithin, Natural Flavors, Cinnamon, Reb A (Derived from the Stevia Plant).
